channel.title: ' Error Connecting to Server '
channel.description:
So whenever I try to login my server it won't let me, it says ' Error Connecting to Server ' Other people can connect, buy why can't I? Can someone please help me... Whenever I go ' Canyouseeme.org ' It says Success: I can see your service on (I BLOCKED MY IP) on port (43594) Your ISP is not blocking port 43594
Thanks to whoever helps me fix this problem ;)

item.title: ' Error Connecting to Server '
item.dc:creator: @Tension_Ltd Tension Ltd
item.description:
@Tension_Ltd wrote:

In your client, you have to change your ip in the client.java file to 127.0.0.1 or 0.0.0.0 and not the no-ip for the server that the players usually log in with.
